Ahti-Veikko Pietarinen (Department of Philosophy, Helsinki)

SUBMISSION DETAILS

We invite submissions of extended abstracts of maximally 8 pages (A4
or letter, 12pt single spaced). The material must be original and
previously unpublished. Parallel submissions to other conferences is
possible but must be indicated with the submission. The material that
is covered in the abstract must be appropriate in length and content
to be presented in a 30-minute talk. Submissions must be made before
*May 15* and sent to one of the following addresses:
Alain.Lecomte@univ-paris8.fr, quatrini@iml.univ-mrs.fr


